{"id":"api/common/DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS","title":"DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS\", \"name\": \"DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/common/src/pipes/date_pipe.ts#L58-L59\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"date_pipe_default_options\">DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS#date_pipe_default_options\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"crskm1tuggmnd21nnf0cjwkan\">允許為應用程式中的 <code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code> 實例提供預設設定的 DI 令牌。該值是一個物件，可以包含以下欄位：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"drcw4uqo7njuj7iwj2zn6lvyw\"><code>dateFormat</code>：設定預設日期格式。如果未提供，<code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code> 將使用 'mediumDate' 作為值。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"59zuy0zp5x4rn56aqn5xagkzs\"><code>timezone</code>：設定預設時區。如果未提供，<code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code> 將使用最終使用者的本地系統時區。</li>\n</ul>\n\n  </section>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/common/DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS\" class=\"code-anchor\">DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS</a>: <a href=\"api/core/InjectionToken\" class=\"code-anchor\">InjectionToken</a>&lt;<a href=\"api/common/DatePipeConfig\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipeConfig</a>&gt;;\n  </code-example>\n\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/DatePipeConfig\"><code>DatePipeConfig</code></a></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n  \n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"eb9eh7ep31pbb3cdr6q6mjauh\">可以透過向此令牌提供具有此介面的值來覆蓋各種日期通道預設值。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4reizjf10jcs1ftw359bt1ndz\">比如：</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8103rqo34pylkuwji16m5e9re\">透過使用令牌提供值來覆蓋預設日期格式：</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nproviders: [\n  {provide: <a href=\"api/common/DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS\" class=\"code-anchor\">DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS</a>, useValue: {dateFormat: 'shortDate'}}\n]\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"63p4oqzo2c5wdd1tansbe38q4\">透過使用令牌提供值來覆蓋預設時區：</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nproviders: [\n  {provide: <a href=\"api/common/DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS\" class=\"code-anchor\">DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS</a>, useValue: {timezone: '-1200'}}\n]\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/DatePipe\n - api/common/DatePipeConfig\n - guide/deprecations\n - guide/update-to-version-15\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS#date_pipe_default_options\n - api/common/DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS#see-also\n - api/common/DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS#usage-notes\n - api/common/DatePipe\n - api/common/DatePipeConfig\n - api/core/InjectionToken\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/common/src/pipes/date_pipe.ts#L58-L59\n-->"}